description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 69, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 207, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, 2 for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30693-51211-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [207 Votes, Top 5% Score]
